[0.012, "o", "DXOS — One binary. Works offline. Free forever.\r\n\r\nUsage: dxos [COMMAND]\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  chat     Interactive chat with the agent\r\n  run      Run a single prompt\r\n  fix      Find and fix issues automatically\r\n  review   Review uncommitted changes\r\n  explain  Explain the current codebase\r\n  test     Run tests and fix failures\r\n  commit   Generate commit message and commit\r\n  pr       Generate PR description and create PR\r\n  setup    Download and configure a model\r\n\r\nNo API key required. Works offline with local models.\r\n"]
