[0.311, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  This is a Rust workspace with 9 crates implementing an AI\r\n  coding agent. The CLI (dxos-cli) provides one-word commands\r\n  like fix, review, and test. The harness crate manages the\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  conversation loop with 3-layer context compression. Tools\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  are native Rust (no subprocesses). Supports Ollama, Anthropic,\r\n  OpenAI, and OpenRouter.\r\n\r\n"]
